# 📊 Security Log Analyzer

A simple C++ application that analyzes login events and reports suspicious login activity.

## Features

- Count successful logins
- Count failed logins
- Generate a security report
- Detect multiple failed login attempts

## Technologies

- C++
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

## How to Compile

```bash
g++ main.cpp -o log-analyzer
```

## Run

```bash
./log-analyzer
```